CF analysis, 10 miles, Aggregated Data

Shunkei Kakimoto

1 Objectives

  • Using well data in the 10 miles buffer, do CF analysis with:
    • Cross-sectional data
      • For LR data, owner-level
      • For TB data, well-level

2 Data

reg_data_10mi_raw <- 
  here("Shared/Data/WaterAnalysis/reg_data_10mi_raw.rds") %>%
  readRDS()

# - Data on TB - #
TB_10mi <- reg_data_10mi_raw[nrdname=="Tri-Basin",]
# - Data on LR - #
LR_10mi <- reg_data_10mi_raw[nrdname=="Lower Republican",]
  • The cross-sectional unit is:
    • For LR data, owner
    • For TB data, well-id
  • About tr=="5_22"
    • In these areas in TB, 9 acre-inches regulation has started from 2009 (the second year of the allocation period 2008-2012)
      • two options for those data points
        • remove entire data points related to tr=="5_22"
        • use only the data points starting from 2009

2.1 Aggragate annual data to whole-periods data by taking mean

2.1.1 LR data

LR_10mi_y_owner <-
  LR_10mi %>%
  .[,.(
    usage = weighted.mean(usage, acres/sum(acres)),
    treat2 = mean(treat2),
    total_acres = sum(acres),
    # --- soil --- #
    silttotal_r = weighted.mean(silttotal_r, acres/sum(acres)),
    claytotal_r = weighted.mean(claytotal_r, acres/sum(acres)),
    slope_r = weighted.mean(slope_r, acres/sum(acres)),
    ksat_r = weighted.mean(ksat_r, acres/sum(acres)),
    awc_r = weighted.mean(awc_r, acres/sum(acres)),
    # --- weather --- #    
    pr_in = weighted.mean(pr_in, acres/sum(acres)),
    pet_in = weighted.mean(pet_in, acres/sum(acres)),
    gdd_in = weighted.mean(gdd_in, acres/sum(acres)),
    # --- tr --- #
    cntyname_fix = unique(cntyname_fix)
  ), by = .(nrd_owner_name, year)]


LR_10mi_owner <- 
  LR_10mi_y_owner %>%
  .[,.(
  usage =  sum(usage),
  treat2 = mean(treat2),
  # --- soil --- #
  silttotal_r = mean(silttotal_r),
  claytotal_r = mean(claytotal_r),
  slope_r = mean(slope_r),
  ksat_r = mean(ksat_r),
  awc_r = mean(awc_r),
  # --- weather --- #  
  pr_in = sum(pr_in),
  pet_in = sum(pet_in),
  gdd_in = sum(gdd_in),
  # --- tr --- #
  cntyname = unique(cntyname_fix)
  ), by = .(nrd_owner_name)] %>%
  .[,nrd_owner_name := NULL]

2.1.2 TB data

TB_10mi_well <-
  TB_10mi %>%
  # remove data points related to tr=="5_22"
  .[tr!="5_22",] %>%
  .[,.(
  usage = sum(usage),
  treat2 = mean(treat2),
  # --- soil --- #
  silttotal_r = mean(silttotal_r),
  claytotal_r = mean(claytotal_r),
  slope_r = mean(slope_r),
  ksat_r = mean(ksat_r),
  awc_r = mean(awc_r),
  # --- weather --- #  
  pr_in = sum(pr_in),
  pet_in = sum(pet_in),
  gdd_in = sum(gdd_in),
  # --- tr --- #
  cntyname = unique(cntyname)
  ), by = .(wellid)] %>%
  .[, names(LR_10mi_owner), with=FALSE]

2.1.3 Regression data

reg_data_10mi <- bind_rows(LR_10mi_owner, TB_10mi_well)

2.2 CF Analysis

2.2.1 1st CF

3 Use owner or well level data that has complete 5 years (from 2008-2012)

# === LR === #
check_comp_LR <- 
  LR_10mi_y_owner[,.(nrd_owner_name, year)] %>%
  .[,index := 1] %>%
  dcast(nrd_owner_name ~ year, value.var = "index") %>%
  imputeTS::na_replace(fill = 0) %>%
  .[, num_y := rowSums(.SD), by = nrd_owner_name]

check_comp_LR[, .N, by = num_y] %>% .[order(num_y)] %>% print()
   num_y   N
1:     1   7
2:     2   1
3:     3   4
4:     4  13
5:     5 613
# select nrd_owner_name who has complete 5 years data
all_y_LR_owner <- check_comp_LR[num_y==5, nrd_owner_name]
# === TB === #
check_comp_TB <- 
  TB_10mi %>%
  .[tr!="5_22", .(wellid, year)] %>%
  .[,index := 1] %>%
  dcast(wellid ~ year, value.var = "index") %>%
  imputeTS::na_replace(fill = 0) %>%
  .[, num_y := rowSums(.SD), by = wellid]

check_comp_TB[, .N, by = num_y] %>% .[order(num_y)] %>% print()
   num_y    N
1:     1   61
2:     2   32
3:     3   48
4:     4   85
5:     5 1131
# select nrd_owner_name who has complete 5 years data
all_y_TB_owner <- check_comp_TB[num_y==5, wellid]
# === LR === #
LR_10mi_owner_comp <- 
  LR_10mi_y_owner[nrd_owner_name %in% all_y_LR_owner,] %>%
  .[,.(
  usage =  sum(usage),
  treat2 = mean(treat2),
  # --- soil --- #
  silttotal_r = mean(silttotal_r),
  claytotal_r = mean(claytotal_r),
  slope_r = mean(slope_r),
  ksat_r = mean(ksat_r),
  awc_r = mean(awc_r),
  # --- weather --- #  
  pr_in = sum(pr_in),
  pet_in = sum(pet_in),
  gdd_in = sum(gdd_in),
  # --- tr --- #
  cntyname = unique(cntyname_fix)
  ), by = .(nrd_owner_name)] %>%
  .[,nrd_owner_name := NULL]

# === TB === #
TB_10mi_well_comp <-
  TB_10mi[wellid %in% all_y_TB_owner,] %>%
  .[,.(
  usage = sum(usage),
  treat2 = mean(treat2),
  # --- soil --- #
  silttotal_r = mean(silttotal_r),
  claytotal_r = mean(claytotal_r),
  slope_r = mean(slope_r),
  ksat_r = mean(ksat_r),
  awc_r = mean(awc_r),
  # --- weather --- #  
  pr_in = sum(pr_in),
  pet_in = sum(pet_in),
  gdd_in = sum(gdd_in),
  # --- tr --- #
  cntyname = unique(cntyname)
  ), by = .(wellid)] %>%
  .[, names(LR_10mi_owner), with=FALSE]
